of types of carbohydrates,

00:22:36.840 --> 00:22:38.090 align:middle line:90%
there's a lot of types of fat.

00:22:38.090 --> 00:22:42.900 align:middle line:84%
So deep fried pork rinds are
not of the same vibration

00:22:42.900 --> 00:22:44.130 align:middle line:90%
