we found that when

00:23:09.960 --> 00:23:13.380 align:middle line:84%
everybody ate fat free salad
dressing and fat free cookies

00:23:13.380 --> 00:23:15.990 align:middle line:84%
that there was usually a lot
more sugar and salt in it,

00:23:15.990 --> 00:23:17.460 align:middle line:84%
