00:23:17.460 --> 00:23:21.270 align:middle line:84%
So fat is a carrier
of flavor, and I

00:23:21.270 --> 00:23:24.330 align:middle line:84%
think it's really about
selecting the good kind of fats

00:23:24.330 --> 00:23:27.180 align:middle line:84%
that are going to be supportive
to your nervous system

00:23:27.180 --> 00:23:30.270 align:middle line:84%
and actually can help satisfy
you so you don't overeat.

00:23:30.270 --> 00:23:32.700 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: There's a lot of
