00:24:17.760 --> 00:24:21.240 align:middle line:84%
but if you're concerned about
cholesterol, eat less red meat.

00:24:21.240 --> 00:24:22.290 align:middle line:90%
Eat less dairy.

00:24:22.290 --> 00:24:26.940 align:middle line:84%
Eat less refined carbohydrates,
and help your liver

00:24:26.940 --> 00:24:29.250 align:middle line:84%
to function better
by using herbs

00:24:29.250 --> 00:24:31.860 align:middle line:84%
that stimulate bile
production, which is

00:24:31.860 --> 00:24:34.290 align:middle line:90%
