00:24:34.290 --> 00:24:36.090 align:middle line:90%
so things like dandelion root.

00:24:36.090 --> 00:24:38.130 align:middle line:84%
And another thing is
to use a little bit

00:24:38.130 --> 00:24:40.110 align:middle line:90%
more the bitter flavor.

00:24:40.110 --> 00:24:44.250 align:middle line:84%
As a culture, we're very
fixated on sweet and salty,

00:24:44.250 --> 00:24:49.020 align:middle line:84%
but when we use the sour flavor,
it helps to activate our liver.

00:24:49.020 --> 00:24:51.420 align:middle line:84%
When we use the
bitter flavor, it

00:24:51.420 --> 00:24:55.500 align:middle line:84%
has a special affinity for our
heart, our small intestines,

00:24:55.500 --> 00:24:57.340 align:middle line:90%
and the liver to some degree.

00:24:57.340 --> 00:24:59.130 align:middle line:84%
So eat a wide
variety of flavors.

00:24:59.130 --> 00:25:03.000 align:middle line:84%
And lemon and water helps
to fluidify the blood.

00:25:03.000 --> 00:25:05.790 align:middle line:84%
