lemon and water?

00:25:11.730 --> 00:25:13.860 align:middle line:90%
It helps to fluidify the blood.

00:25:13.860 --> 00:25:17.160 align:middle line:84%
And there's also a
whole array of plants

00:25:17.160 --> 00:25:21.750 align:middle line:84%
