and red ant bites.

00:26:31.110 --> 00:26:33.390 align:middle line:10%
So getting stung with
nettles is actually

00:26:33.390 --> 00:26:37.515 align:middle line:10%
really therapeutic
for arthritic joints.

00:26:37.515 --> 00:26:39.390 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: I get stung with
