00:27:08.760 --> 00:27:11.299 align:middle line:90%
and we also know that nettles--

00:27:11.299 --> 00:27:12.840 align:middle line:84%
and I want to be
clear, because there

00:27:12.840 --> 00:27:14.520 align:middle line:90%
are a lot of stinging plants--

00:27:14.520 --> 00:27:19.380 align:middle line:90%
urtica dioica or urtica urens--

00:27:19.380 --> 00:27:21.810 align:middle line:84%
