and adrenal exhaustion?

00:27:30.660 --> 00:27:35.160 align:middle line:84%
So nettles can help relieve some
of the symptoms of allergies.

00:27:35.160 --> 00:27:38.070 align:middle line:84%
Nettles is really
strengthening to our bones.

00:27:38.070 --> 00:27:41.730 align:middle line:84%
I mean, women are concerned
about not getting osteoporosis

00:27:41.730 --> 00:27:45.150 align:middle line:84%
later on, and nettles
made as an overnight tea

00:27:45.150 --> 00:27:48.587 align:middle line:84%
is a wonderful, delicious,
mineral rich brew.

00:27:48.587 --> 00:27:50.670 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Is the best thing
to do when we find herbs

00:27:50.670 --> 00:27:51.470 align:middle line:90%
