I always ask my guests,
what is your biggest

00:54:46.280 --> 00:54:47.890 align:middle line:90%
why for doing what you do?

00:54:47.890 --> 00:54:50.780 align:middle line:84%
What motivates you to do
all of this incredible work

00:54:50.780 --> 00:54:52.580 align:middle line:90%
in the world?

00:54:52.580 --> 00:54:54.290 align:middle line:90%
>>MARS: I feel so blessed.

