If I get to help the
planet and people,

00:54:59.820 --> 00:55:03.720 align:middle line:84%
I feel like I'm doing what
I was called here to do,

00:55:03.720 --> 00:55:07.420 align:middle line:84%
and every day my
prayer is help me

00:55:07.420 --> 00:55:12.910 align:middle line:84%
to help make a positive
difference in the world.

00:55:12.910 --> 00:55:16.390 align:middle line:84%
And if I can show people that
they can have better health

00:55:16.390 --> 00:55:20.350 align:middle line:84%
and at the same time be
better stewards of the Earth,

00:55:20.350 --> 00:55:21.760 align:middle line:90%
that does it for me.

00:55:21.760 --> 00:55:23.290 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Then you're fulfilled.

